Specification: LSB Core Generic
Specification: LSB Core IA32, IA64, PPC32, PPC64, S390, S390X, AMD64
Edition of Specification: 3.1 Update 1
Type: Error
Status: Unapproved
Bug reference: http://bugs.linuxbase.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1311

Rationale: the global data interfaces in6addr_any and in6addr_loopback,
documented in ISO POSIX (2003) were omitted.


In LSB Core Generic:

In 13.3.8. Socket Interface

Add 

   Table 13-14. libc - Socket Interface Data Interfaces
   in6addr_any [SUSv3] in6addr_loopback [SUSv3]


13.4.24. netinet/in.h

extern const struct in6_addr in6addr_any;
extern const struct in6_addr in6addr_loopback;


In Appendix A. Alphabetical Listing of Interfaces,

In A.1. libc,

in Table A-2. libc Data Interfaces, 

Insert

   in6addr_any[SUSv3] in6addr_loopback[SUSv3]

